{"tid":84180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"通脹近1600% 委內瑞拉印新鈔應對","createTime":"2017-01-17T10:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T13:50:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b05ba6bb86283389cdbd4a0640c9c1e5d3e7fea","tid":84180,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"委內瑞拉通脹近1600%　推3款新鈔應對 <br />\n2017-01-17 HKT 16:27 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1308138_1_L_20170117171152.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1308138_1_L_20170117171152.jpg&h=5cb8778a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n委內瑞拉推出全新面值的鈔票，圖為500玻利瓦爾的新鈔。（美聯社） <br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉推出全新面值500至2萬玻利瓦爾新鈔票，以應對當地今年預期近百分之1600的通脹率。 <br />\n<br />\n民眾在銀行門外排隊換領新鈔，不過有民眾指，2萬玻利瓦爾的黑市兌換價折合少於6美元，對日常購物及壓抑通脹作用不大。 <br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉政府去年底為了打擊不法石油產品勾當，一度宣佈廢除原先最大面值100玻利瓦爾紙幣，引發國內不滿。 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1308138-20170117.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1308138-20170117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=txGxP0W71hYQd4d9YDo6UksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=557ef771\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1308138-20170117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dc4688fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1308138-20170117.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3fbcf14d2037c93e1cee1e1fb5bef44e30ff4fbc","tid":84180,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"這是委內瑞拉的新鈔票：多了幾個零、豎著的 <br />\n<br />\n在經歷各種困難後，委內瑞拉週一終於迎來了自己的新版玻利瓦爾。新版玻利瓦爾較老版多了幾個零，並且版面是垂直的。 <br />\n一名35歲的售貨員Milena Molina說：「我從未想過我會拿到這麼大面值的鈔票，現在買東西比以前方便很多，再也不用擰著個大袋子到處跑了。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/mw690/e73cbe62gw1fbtr80yd7qj20f50edq3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2Fe73cbe62gw1fbtr80yd7qj20f50edq3d.jpg&h=6e7d031f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ffe220b24c43c0356d9f74756bcc9576eda8cf6","tid":84180,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:56:28.000Z","msg":"一日繼續印，通脹唔會停<br />\n係方便咗唔洗拎成堆銀紙買野"},{"pid":"7ef35bd952e326e0b8667594c0ea5c19d36c2076","tid":84180,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"都係解決唔到問題"},{"pid":"d8011ffedcad9bd34b74780bda9cbe5ae3c668a1","tid":84180,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"我可以接受1個委妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d514ca08eecc387d6cdfe77c3ed5c115ba831da","tid":84180,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"就快另一個大國會發生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211eac22f9b90bbc612b817d72dd40a2a697121f","tid":84180,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/dreamyeh/normal_4a2f5b61c4a38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fdreamyeh%2Fnormal_4a2f5b61c4a38.jpg&h=df49389f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5c7cb04c830cba164f9bec4505f0746a93d3987","tid":84180,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:45:30.000Z","msg":"開始一罐午餐肉，有西吊架時代來臨！"},{"pid":"360e12e8169417016fb508ff11bb2e832357f945","tid":84180,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:49:22.000Z","msg":"打直既銀紙幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dacd97d340f9d3a1ecfce7f6d3c523169d694435","tid":84180,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:50:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打直既銀紙幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個 design OK 喎"}]}